{"title":"照亮","date":"2018-07-08T10:38:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2018年7月8日","L":"2018/07/08","MM-DD":"07-08"},"thumbnail":"https://i.loli.net/2019/12/12/iO8YBDmfgteGuRh.jpg","link":"2018/07/08/照亮","comments":true,"tags":["诗"],"categories":["诗"],"updated":"2020-01-09T17:48:37.984Z","content":"<p>每粒尘埃\n每颗星体\n都默然地牵引</p>\n<p>缓缓转动\n落满银河\n在悬臂上斑驳闪耀</p>\n<p>渺如星火\n微不足道\n但灯\n一盏便足以照亮一切</p>\n<p>烟花芳华瞬逝\n青柏残留千古\n撒一片阴凉</p>\n","prev":{"title":"枫","link":"2018/11/15/枫"},"next":{"title":"到站了","link":"2018/04/30/到站了"},"plink":"http://wardzhou.art/2018/07/08/照亮/","reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"白桦树下的人","link":"<a href=\"http://wardzhou.art/2018/07/08/照亮/\" title=\"照亮\">http://wardzhou.art/2018/07/08/照亮/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}